Title: Sphere Scratcher Pro
Body (HTML): Sphere Scratcher PRO, with its new design which makes it even cuter can be used for grinding cat's claws and teeth. It is an attractive and functional scratching surface for feline pets. This Fun, Sustainable & Interactive toy can entertain even the laziest cat for hours, keeping him away from boredom. With the Sphere Scratcher, you can be guaranteed your cat will grow active, and healthy. Benefits: Transforms your cat's life (and yours!): this quality made and super cute scratcher helps prevent the cat from scratching and damaging furniture and other things at home. This will also pair perfectly in every room of your house. Stable, durable woven sisal rope, made to stand the toughest claw, paw and scratches: no flimsy fabric or chenille, the wooden base and the fact that the scratching posts are securely fixed on both ends allow the structure to be firm when your cat uses it for its nails. Healthy & Happy Feline Friend The Sphere Scratcher encourages activity to help improve physical and mental health.
